{
 "name": "RPlog_Shopping_Sightseeing_Fighting_off_Thugs",
 "title": "Shopping, Sightseeing, Fighting off Thugs",
 "summary": "On the Caspian mountain town of Marin, the Jedi student Orson Tighe and his teacher and love Jessalyn Valios browse a swoop shop, where Orson quietly orders her an expert-level repulsorboard and fends off a couple of flirting Sarian salesmen out of unexpected jealousy. Strolling afterward, Orson confesses his unease at having used the Force to read a lying Griffon, wrestling with the ethics of wielding such power for profit on Karrde's behalf, and Jessalyn gently reassures him. Their walk takes them past an eerie forest temple where two thugs -- a blaster-wielding human and a vibroblade-armed Rodian -- ambush them; Jessalyn deflects the blaster bolts with her lightsaber while Orson disarms and throws the Rodian using his new skills. The attackers driven off, a shaken Jessalyn struggles with a strange new fear while Orson reflects on the lesson of letting the Force guide him rather than forcing it, and the two retreat from the woods together.",
